title: Lufthansa flights expected to return to normal following strike injunction
text:
Lufthansa flights expected to return to normal following strike injunction Original,   
Sep 10, 2015 eTN   
Germany's biggest airline has said that service should be back to normal after a court ordered striking pilots back to work. The court granted Lufthansa a temporary injunction against the work stoppage. 
A Lufthansa spokesperson said early on Thursday that Germany's flag carrier airline anticipated no further disruptions to its regular flight schedule. "We expect normal flight service without any cancellations," the spokesperson said. Source: DW
